Description: Simple CA intended for use with Let's Connect! and eduVPN
 A simple Certification Authority for TLS/SSL server certificates,
 offering a tiny CLI API for use with Let's Connect! software from
 https://letsconnect-vpn.org/ and in the eduVPN project
 at https://www.eduvpn.nl/.
